abstract: Vivien Schweitzer reviews performance by violinist Alexi Kenney at Weill Recital Hall.
lead_paragraph: Mr. Kenney’s program included a Westhoff suite for solo violin, a Schumann sonata, a Shawn Jaeger premiere and a partner, the pianist Renana Gutman.

headline.main: Review: Alexi Kenney at Weill Recital Hall
headline.print_headline: Liquid Trills, Turbulence and an Ode to the Soil
